basic.description:
{Basic Archery}

Basic Archery increases damage dealt by ranged creatures by 15% and increases their maximum shots by 1.

With Artillery, Ballista and Cannon can receive matching Archery bonuses based on both skill levels.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Archery}

Advanced Archery increases damage dealt by ranged creatures by 25%, increases their maximum shots by 2, and extends full-damage shooting range by 1 hex.

With Artillery, Ballista and Cannon can receive matching Archery bonuses based on both skill levels.

expert.description:
{Expert Archery}

Expert Archery increases damage dealt by ranged creatures by 50%, increases their maximum shots by 3, extends full-damage shooting range by 1 hex, and makes their ranged attacks inflict Basic Forgetfulness on the target.

With Artillery, Ballista and Cannon can receive matching Archery bonuses based on both skill levels.
